wiki.summary: In a brief interview on American Idol host Ryan Seacrest's radio show on October 31, 2007, Britney said her favorite Blackout song is "Heaven on Earth." Said Spears: "It's a cool track. It's like, I love the producers who did that and it's kind of different from all the other songs." Heaven on EarthBritney Spears
